to run, type:
        make
        ./mutantaliens
hjklyubn to move. arrow keys work for orthogonal movement. keypad not yet implemented.
r to check radio signal strength.
f to enter fire mode, hjklyubn or arrow keys to target, f to fire, i to inspect targeted square.
d to enter debug mode. not half as fun as the average debug mode.
X,Y,Z to wield pistol, rifle, plasma cannon.